<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.2.9">
<l>cintap puṭaittuc ceṅkuru tikoṇṭu pūtaṅkaḷ</l>
<l>antip palikoṭut tāvat taṉamceyap paṉmalai</l>
<l>yinti rakōpaṅkaḷ emperumāṉ kaṉivā yoppāṉ</l>
<l>cintum puṟavil teṉtiru māliruñ cōlaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of [our] father that gives succor in [times of] adversity,</l>
<l rend="indent">as demons gather up the red blood that scatters and swells</l>
<l rend="indent">giving [it] as an offering at dusk,</l>
<l>is Tirumāliruñcōlai in the South</l>
<l rend="indent">where Indragōpa beetles spill out through the forest</l>
<l rend="indent">so that they resemble the ripe fruit lips of our lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
